title.narrative: Case management and referral mechanisms are in place to respond to the protection needs of children

description.narrative: Application of case management in child protection and quality of child protection specialized services for children needing specialized assistance improved in 11 governorates. As a result, 17,646 (110% of target) children received child protection services like PSS, Family Tracing and Reunification, referrals to other services and cash assistance. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:19/01/2020
